8  Safety Requirements
    	8.1  	The system shall be approved by the PEPA.
          8.1.1 The system shall be officially validated by the PEPA to ensure that the system doesn’t violate any environmental laws.
          
      	8.2   	The system shall be approved by the MNHSRC.
           8.2.1   The system shall be officially validated by the MNHSRC to ensure that the system doesn’t violate any health regulations.
           
        8.3  The system shall be approved by the FBR.
           8.3.1	 The system shall be officially validated by FBR to ensure that the system’s revenue generation stream doesn’t violate any financial laws and that the taxation system is properly followed.
